article_title: Wal-Mart Executive to Join Discount Retailer Five Below
article_text:
Five Below Inc. said Tuesday that Joel Anderson, the chief executive of Walmart.com in the U.S., will become president of the teen-focused discount retailer next month.

Mr. Anderson will lead all aspects of merchandising, stores and marketing, Five Below...
